title: Kevin's Supersized Salvage Airbus A320 Documentary
description: Kevin’s Supersized Salvage: Airbus A320 Kevin McCloud challenges three designers to turn one plane - an Airbus A320 - into hundreds of amazing new products in a giant upcycling experiment. Their task is to find a new use for every single piece of the plane, leaving only an empty hangar behind them
